ratio is a technical banking

00:11:19.069 --> 00:11:20.689
term about managing funds.

00:11:20.780 --> 00:11:23.569
Nothing to do with
customer deposits via UPI.

00:11:24.020 --> 00:11:26.839
The correct initiative
is UPI enhancements.

00:11:27.260 --> 00:11:32.089
This specific feature, allowing cash
deposits through UPI is one of the recent

00:11:32.120 --> 00:11:37.250
upgrades made to the UPI system to expand
its capabilities beyond just payments.

00:11:37.579 --> 00:11:38.150
Thank you.

